South African National Blood Service was celebrating World Blood Donor Day. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The South African National Blood Service says the greatest gift is the gift of life. SANBS says donor blood is used everyday to save lives. The service is celebrating World Blood Donor Day. READ: SANBS takes blood delivery to the sky South Africans are being urged to go out in their numbers to donate, to maintain a stable supply of safe blood. The SANBS is raising awareness about the importance of donating blood and it is also using a unique service to access hard to reach places. South African National Blood Service was celebrating World Blood Donor Day. Courtesy #DStv403